1.first create a ansible.cfg in /tmp directory
2. create ansible.cfg in your project directory
3. create .ansible.cfg in your home directory
4. create ansible.cfg in /etc/ansible

export ANSIBLE_CONFIG=/tmp/ansible.cfg

Try testing now

ansible --version; what whould you be able to see as default configurtion file?
remove ansible.cfg file you created and see how defaults ansible.cfg value being changed.
